@AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5159
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_FROM_AUTH_LOGIN

### ── Adverse Events ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all adverse events
GET {{AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress}}/api/adverse-events?skip=0&take=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter by protocol and severity
GET {{AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress}}/api/adverse-events?protocolId=1&severity=Severe
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter by status
GET {{AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress}}/api/adverse-events?status=UnderReview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get adverse event by id
GET {{AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress}}/api/adverse-events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Report a new adverse event
POST {{AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress}}/api/adverse-events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": 1,
  "protocolId": 1,
  "siteId": 1,
  "reportedByUserId": 3,
  "severity": "Moderate",
  "category": "Gastrointestinal",
  "description": "Patient reported nausea and vomiting 48h post-dose.",
  "occurredAt": "2026-07-10T14:00:00Z",
  "reportedAt": "2026-07-11T09:00:00Z"
}

### Update adverse event (e.g. move to UnderReview)
PUT {{AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress}}/api/adverse-events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "severity": "Moderate",
  "category": "Gastrointestinal",
  "description": "Patient reported nausea and vomiting 48h post-dose.",
  "occurredAt": "2026-07-10T14:00:00Z",
  "reportedAt": "2026-07-11T09:00:00Z",
  "status": "UnderReview",
  "resolution": null
}

### Resolve an adverse event
PUT {{AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress}}/api/adverse-events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "severity": "Moderate",
  "category": "Gastrointestinal",
  "description": "Patient reported nausea and vomiting 48h post-dose.",
  "occurredAt": "2026-07-10T14:00:00Z",
  "reportedAt": "2026-07-11T09:00:00Z",
  "status": "Resolved",
  "resolution": "Symptoms resolved within 72h. No dose adjustment required."
}

### Soft-delete adverse event (Admin only)
DELETE {{AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress}}/api/adverse-events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── Deviations ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all deviations
GET {{AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress}}/api/deviations?skip=0&take=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter deviations by protocol and type
GET {{AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress}}/api/deviations?protocolId=1&type=Major
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get deviation by id
GET {{AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress}}/api/deviations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Report a new deviation
POST {{AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress}}/api/deviations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": 1,
  "protocolId": 1,
  "siteId": 1,
  "reportedByUserId": 3,
  "type": "Minor",
  "description": "Visit window exceeded by 3 days due to patient scheduling conflict.",
  "occurredAt": "2026-07-08T00:00:00Z",
  "reportedAt": "2026-07-11T10:00:00Z"
}

### Update deviation
PUT {{AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress}}/api/deviations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "Minor",
  "description": "Visit window exceeded by 3 days due to patient scheduling conflict.",
  "occurredAt": "2026-07-08T00:00:00Z",
  "reportedAt": "2026-07-11T10:00:00Z",
  "status": "Resolved",
  "correctiveAction": "Patient rescheduling SOP updated to include 48h buffer reminder."
}

### Soft-delete deviation (Admin only)
DELETE {{AdverseEvent.API_HostAddress}}/api/deviations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
